1983;;Winds of War;;American;;Dan Curtis;;Robert Mitchum, Ali MacGraw, John Houseman, Polly Bergen, Jan-Michael Vincent;;war, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Winds_of_War_(TV_miniseries);;The film follows the plot of Wouk's novel closely, depicting events from March 1939 until the entry of the United States into World War II in December 1941. It tells the story of Victor "Pug" Henry, and his family, and their relationships with a mixture of real people and fictional characters. Henry is a Naval Officer and friend of President Franklin Delano Roosevelt.